quebee - a blog for social SQL query writers

Overview:

Gives SQL query users a means to share and understand SQL queries in a large organization.

* Front Page
** Recent Queries
** Currently running Queries
** Top Rated Queries
** Top Queries
** Top Query Writers
** Top Query Runners (daily top query runners)
** Top Database Users (daily top DB time used)
** Login

* User
** URI: user/:id
** Blog
** Favorite Queries
** Last N Queries Written
** Last N Queries Ran
** Queue of Queries Pending

* Query
** URI: query/:id
** Name
** Description
** Database
** Last execution
** Related queries
** Tags
** Parent query
** Version
** Votes
*** Usefulness
*** Efficiency
*** Correctness

* Query Parameter
** URI: query_parameter/:id
** Name
** Description
** Default
** Type
** Valid Set (from list or query?)

** Query Schedule
*** User(s)
*** Date / Time
*** Query
*** Notification
*** Email results?

** Query Execution
** URI: query_execution/:id
*** Query
*** Who
*** When
*** Server
*** Status
**** Queued
**** Running
**** Errored
**** Aborted
**** Finished

** Query Results
** URI: query_results/:id
*** Pagination
*** Columns
*** Export to CSV
*** Stats - Time, # Rows Returned
*** Comments
**** Who
**** When
**** Comment

* Database
** URI: database/:id
** Name
** Description
** Schema
** Server(s)

* Server
** URI: server/:id
** Name
** Description
** Queue Depth
** Pending in Queue
** Master / Slave

* Schema
** URI: schema/:id
** Name
** Description
** Table / Views
*** Name
*** Description
**** Columns
***** Name
***** Description
***** Type
***** FK/PK


